metadata.description:
MM Creature 1
Magic Mushroom Creatures is a unique and imaginative exploration into the surreal world as seen through the eyes of an artist who is also an avid mushroom enthusiast. This collection of enchanting artworks by digital artist Kevin Knight captivates a visual perspective that matches and transcends their natural counterparts. These exquisite works are a blend of abstract expressionism, psychedelic realism, and surrealism.
